<section id="welcome" class="py-24 reveal">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-5 gap-16 md:gap-20 items-center">
      <div class="md:col-span-3">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-6 text-black font-semibold">Welcome</h2>
        <div class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
          <p>
            Celeste is a dedicated Yoga teacher known for her passion of movement and wellbeing.
            Specialising in Rocket<sup class="text-xs">™</sup>, Ashtanga and Vinyasa, classes are
            created to be an inclusive space that invite you to come as you are and do what you can,
            recognising that each day, each body and each practice can be different.
          </p>
          <p>
            Celeste&rsquo;s classes offer students the opportunity to explore their physical
            potential, create mental spaciousness and develop a deeper connection to self.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative h-96 md:h-[500px] w-full md:col-span-2">
        <img
          src="/images/extra.jpg"
          alt="Celeste — yoga practice"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover object-bottom opacity-80"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
